    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "And on the morrow, John stood there"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "And spoke to two or three."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "And as he lifted up his eyes,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "He then did Jesus see."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "He said, “Behold the Lamb of God,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "’Tis He Who walks this way."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "He’s here to take the sins of all"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "And bear them all away!”"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Yet poor religion counted not"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "These things of any worth,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "But seeking for a leader great"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "It lingered on in dearth;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "And looking for a movement strong,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Continued in its strife."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Preoccupied with all these things,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "They missed the Lord of LIFE!"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Religion is Christ’s enemy,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "It’s even so today."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "For though they name Him, should He come,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "They’d put the Lord away."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "They did it then, they’d do it now,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "They’d miss the Lord again."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "So let us seek the Lord Himself,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "The lamb, the dove obtain."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Now in the Lord’s recovery"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "We’re drawn to Christ alone."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "The Spirit as the gentle dove"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Has found in us a home."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Let all religion turn away"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "To movements wide and great;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "This testimony of Himself"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Our Lord will vindicate!"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
